column4:
This is my first time writing here, so I hope I get it right. I'm not sure how to do this, so here goes. 
 
 It's so easy to understand this line of writing. It'll be easy to be good at. 1. I want to be able to write in a way that's easy to read and understand. 2. It will be easy for me to understand. I do n't want to have to think about my words so much. 3. I will be able, in the future, to be better at this. 4. I hope to be.

The calculator is a tool of calculation. 
 It is an instrument of science and math. 



The poet is a skill of poetry. 


It is a means of expression, of art and of creation. 




It is an art of words and the power of language. 





The calculator can find a rhyme and the poet can find an equation.
